msgid "Module system deep dive"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:4
msgid "Or: *Wrapping the world in modules*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:6
msgid ""
"In this tutorial you will follow an extensive demonstration of how to wrap "
"an existing API with Nix modules."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:8
msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:10
msgid ""
"This tutorial follows [@infinisil](https://github.com/infinisil)'s "
"[presentation on modules](https://infinisil.com/modules.mp4)  ([source]"
"(https://github.com/tweag/summer-of-nix-modules)) for  participants of "
