#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:14
msgid "What will you learn?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:16
msgid ""
"You'll write modules to interact with the [Google Maps API](https://"
"developers.google.com/maps/documentation/maps-static), declaring module "
