#: ../../../tutorials/module-system/deep-dive.md:26
msgid ""
"To run the examples in this tutorial, you will need a [Google API key]"
"(https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/maps-static/start#before-"
"you-begin) in `$XDG_DATA_HOME/google-api/key`."
